SoftEther VPN -> Multi-Protocol VPN software
--------------------------------------------
(x) Alternative to OpenVPN
(x) Realize BYOD (Bring Your Own Device) on business -> Smartphones, Tablets or Laptops 
(x) Built in L2TP Client connect to SoftEther-VPN server -> Remote Access 
(x) Strong resistance against firewalls -> Any deep-packet inspection firewalls cannot reach transport packets
(x) SoftEther VPN uses Ethernet over HTTPS for camouflage
(x) Can Setup a VPN-Server behind the Enterpise Firewall 
(x)  
